videos.description: Saint Mary's Tommy Kuhse comes up with a big block on Antwan Kimmons, then he sets up Logan Johnson for a 3-pointer in the corner on the other end.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Kuhse's block leads to Saint Mary's 3-pointer) 2020/11/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kuhse's block leads to Saint Mary's 3-pointer

videos.description: Just before halftime, Northern Iowa's AJ Green comes off a screen at the top of the key and drains a 3-pointer over a Saint Mary's defender to extend the Panthers' lead to 39-31.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (AJ Green splashes 3-pointer on Saint Mary's defender) 2020/11/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: AJ Green splashes 3-pointer on Saint Mary's defender

videos.description: Tommy Kuhse ties the game with a difficult off-balance layup, then hits the go-ahead bucket in the final seconds of Saint Mary's comeback win over Northern Iowa.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Kuhse hits two clutch shots in Saint Mary's win) 2020/11/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kuhse hits two clutch shots in Saint Mary's win
